originalText.text: Kenn is the best!! This was my very first deep tissue massage and it was such a pleasant experience. Kenn is truly an expert at what he does, he made me feel relaxed and made sure I was comfortable the entire time. I had very little soreness the following day and felt like a brand new woman! I will definitely be back for my next massage with Kenn. If you do decide to work with Kenn, it will totally be worth it.

originalText.text: I get massages frequently and often leave feeling dissatisfied - this massage hit the mark. It was actual bodywork rather than just being rubbed (which I acknowledge can also feel good and be relaxing while it’s happening). Kenn uses pressure and gets the fascia to actually release (improved muscle performance/circulation which means decreased pain and tension). A day later my muscles feel blissed out. Kenn is professional and kind and was present throughout the entire massage. I will definitely go back!

originalText.text: I was introduced to Kenneth by a mutual friend who is an dancer/actor undergoing a long and physical run. He recommended Kenneth's work as the "greatest massage he has received in New York City", which coming from that guy, means everything. So I purchased a session as a gift to my friend and co-worker N, who was hurting after work a long strenuous project of mine. N was overjoyed by the results and reported feeling the blissful effects many days after the session and his work, already brilliant, was performed with even more élan. I quickly purchased N another session and N came back with the words "That was the greatest massage I have ever had." And N has had MANY massages in his time. I am looking forward to gifting myself a session, and have recommended him to other friends who are eager to book a session. Kenneth, you helped my friend, which helped my project, which helped me! Deep Massage IS the Best Massage in New York City!

originalText.text: Kenn is an amazing massage therapist. Every time I find myself in NYC, I ensure I make at least one visit. He is super-intuitive, and knows exactly how to provide relief from both chronic pain and tired muscles.  I could not recommend him highly enough.

originalText.text: I am in the final weeks of planning a wedding, in the first couple weeks of a new job at work, and working out like crazy to fit perfectly in my wedding dress... Needless to say, I'm stressed, and my body needed some relaxation!  This was definitely one of the best massages I've ever received.  I asked for a strong deep tissue, and boy was it!  If you like a strong deep tissue, this is definitely the best.  I'm sure he can do lighter too (so don't be worried if you don't like the strong pressure kind), but I specifically asked for a lot of pressure and he did great.  I already told my fiancé to go, and I definitely plan to return again myself!  I highly recommend you do too!
